data.description: Willow Springs - As Sweet as can be, this Adorable Home embraced by Beautiful Magnolias is looking for its new owner. Enjoy Upgrades Galore as you marvel at all of the updates made in this wonderful property. Prepare meals like a pro with this New Kitchen Range with plenty of couterspace. Your Primary Suite is your sanctuary & this one has New plumbing in the Shower, & New Flooring. You'll be comfy & cozy with the New HVAC & (2) new Eccobee thermostats. Relax on the New Deck with Gazebo, don't miss a single game or program, the gazebo already has a mount ready to accept your TV. The fenced-in yard is flat and usable. All New Exterior Siding & Shakes. Freshly Painted Interior. All toilets replaced. Painted vanities. New Surge Protector in Electrical Panel. $10K+ Water Filtration System. Riding mower can convey with Acceptable Offer. You'll love this Sweet Charmer.
